skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: c. t. a. bot
des:
No setup required! Just ask c. t. a. bot to lookup arrival times for your bus or train.

Train times can be looked up using a line and a station name. For example:

'Alexa, ask c. t. a. bot when the next train from western o'hare is.'

Bus times need to be looked up using an intersection and a direction. For example:

'Alexa, ask c. t. a. bot when the next bus at fullerton and kedzie eastbound is'
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
